               <msContents class="#CM">
                  <summary>Bound codex, containing folios of various measurements and paper. Contains handwritten notes by Edouard Ariel, that is, translations in French from the Tamil, Sanskrit, and Telugu.
There were originally various bundles, each contained in a folded folio bearing title and often a date (these folded folios also bear library foliation). For some texts, instead of translations, we find rather a list of vocabulary. Various notes are often inserted.
                  </summary>
                  
